name: Burner #2: Flipper Burner
description:
Life: 4, Speed: 3, Damage: 3

Behavior: The Flipper Burner shoots back at you. Hidden behind FOMO Burners, they can't hold for too long. Therefore, some of them might not aim much and throw what they got at you. Others might be smarter, wait, observe and hit you in your future position. Hope your tezuru are well-positioned to survive their flipping touch.

Utility: Collect all 5 Burners to add +1 Damage to all your Tezurus.
